[SHORT DESC]
Has a high critical hit rate.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a critical hit rate one stage higher than normal. Assuming there are no other critical hit modifiers in play, this move has a 1/8 chance to get a critical hit instead of a 1/16 chance.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Razor Leaf should not be used competitively. Its Base Power and distribution are both too low, plus it is outclassed by stronger moves, such as Giga Drain and Leaf Blade.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/seed_bomb">Seed Bomb</a> is a competitive alternative with 80 Base Power.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/leaf_blade">Leaf Blade</a> is a stronger alternative with 90 Base Power.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/wood_hammer">Wood Hammer</a> is a stronger alternative with 120 Base Power, but causes recoil damage.</p>